TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Sql Query
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: SELECT SRC_ORDERS.ORDER_ID, SRC_ORDERS.CUSTOMER_ID, SRC_ORDERS.ORDER_STATUS, SRC_ORDERS.ORDER_DATE, SRC_ORDERS.REQUIRED_DATE, SRC_ORDERS.SHIPPED_DATE, SRC_ORDERS.STORE_ID, SRC_ORDERS.STAFF_ID FROM SRC_ORDERS where SRC_ORDERS.ORDER_DATE > TO_DATE( '$$V_LAST_RUN', 'MM/DD/YYYY HH24:MI:SS')
